+ *  19/10/05, Complete lockless mechanism.
+ *  27/05/05, Modular redesign and rewrite.
+ *
+ * Userspace reader semantic :
+ * while (poll fd != POLLHUP) {
+ *   - ioctl RELAY_GET_SUBBUF_SIZE
